        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "long prayers",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Such as the twenty-six forms of prayer at ablution; the Eighteen Benedictions (Shemoneh Esreh), &c.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
