        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "Bleeders",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ",' so mock-modest that, because they will not raise their eyes, they run against walls, etc. Thus the Jewish writers themselves depict the Pharisees as the Tartuffes of antiquity\" (Farrar). ",
        "children": []
      },
